## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible pathways to development. The dynamic nature of global economics means that strategies effective today may not be applicable in the future. Additionally, the socio-political context of each country can significantly influence the effectiveness of these strategies, which may not be fully captured in this report.

